## 6. Data Model & Database

### 10 Core Entities

```mermaid
erDiagram
    Building ||--o{ Floor : contains
    Floor ||--o{ Area : contains
    Floor ||--o{ Device : "has installed"
    Department ||--o| Employee : "managed by"
    Employee }o--|| Department : "belongs to"
    Employee }o--|| Shift : "assigned to"
    Employee ||--o{ AttendanceEvent : triggers
    Device ||--o{ AttendanceEvent : captures
    Employee ||--o{ PresenceSession : tracked
    Area ||--o{ PresenceSession : "session in"
    User ||--|| Employee : "login for"
```

