| [003_add_keycloak_identity.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/003_add_keycloak_identity.sql) | Keycloak subject ID column |
| [003_keycloak_migration.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/003_keycloak_migration.sql) | Keycloak-specific auth columns |
| [004_add_pgvector.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/004_add_pgvector.sql) | Vector extension for face embeddings |
| [005_create_devices_table.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/005_create_devices_table.sql) | Edge device registry |
| [006_create_device_events_table.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/006_create_device_events_table.sql) | Device telemetry events |
| [007_create_attendance_events_table.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/007_create_attendance_events_table.sql) | Face recognition attendance logs |
| [008_create_employee_faces_table.sql](file:///c:/Yash/FRS/backend/src/db/migrations/008_create_employee_faces_table.sql) | Enrolled face data storage |

